    PHP Need to Know:

 Array Operations:

1) array_change_key_case($array,CASE_LOWER)
2) array_diff($a1,$a2) - returns the difference between 2 arrays as an array
3) array_filter($a1,"$string") - returns array of keyWord string
4) array_intersect($a1,$a2) - returns matching array
5) array_keys($a), array_key_exists("key",$array) - returns all keys, if key exist in array
6) array_map("myfunction",$a) - returns an array of different structure 
7) array_merge($a1,$a2) - joins 2 or more arrays 
8) array_replace($a1,$a2), array_replace_recursive() - replace array values
9) array_search("word",$a) - search an array for key word 
10) array_shift($a) - Permanently Removes first element of array, returns value of removed element
11) array_slice($a,int amountOfIndex,int amountOfIndex) - remove indexs starting from index Zero
12) array_multisort($a1,SORT_ASC,$a2,SORT_DESC) - Sort an Array 
13) array_reverse($a) - Reverse an array 
14) array_splice($a1,int startIndex, int amountToReplaced ,$a2) - Permanently replace 
15) array_unique($a) - Permanently removes duplicate indexs
16) arsort($a), asort() - sort a Named array in desc and Asc order 
17) compact('stringVariableName', 'stringVariableName') - create array using string variables
18) count($cars) - returns total elements within an Array
19) array_unshift($a,"blue") - Add element to front of Array
20)  current(), end(), next(), prev(), reset() - Array Traversal 




String Operations: 

1) strlen ($string) - string lenght 
2) str_word_count($string) - counts the number of words in a paragrah 
3) strrev($string) - string reverse 
4) strpos($string, 'key') - string position
5) str_replace ('search', 'replace', $string)
6) explode(" ", $string) - breaks a string into an array 
7) implode($string=array($string, $string)) - joins an array into a string
8) htmlspecialchars($str) -  stop html code in string from executing 
9) similar_text($string,$string) - returns amount of similarity 
10) strcasecmp(), strcmp() - string compare case-insensitive and case sensitive 
11) str_split($string) - breaks a single string into an array 
12) strstr($string,"word") - finds and returns all occurance of a string inside another string
13) substr($string,int start,int end) - sub string
14) substr_count($string, 'word') - the amount of time a sub string occurs in another string
15) strtolower($string) -	Converts a string to lowercase letters



